dc_title_s: Williams and Bushnell's new map of Florida; compiled from the surveys of the U.S. Central Land Office, the U.S. coast surveys, private surveys, and other original sources by Arthur T. Williams and John W. Bushnell; drawn by F.C. Rotxoll.; New map of Florida
dc_description_s: Hand colored. Inset: Map of the western portion of Florida. 1 map: hand col.; 147 x 109 cm., on sheet 155 x 115 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
dc_creator_sm: Williams, Arthur T.,Bushnell, John W.,Rotxoll, F. C.,Welcke, Robert A.,Williams & Bushnell.
